The current `connectGmail` endpoint returns a Unipile hosted auth URL. Since the CLI already handles Gmail OAuth locally (via the YAML connector definition) and pushes the encrypted refresh token to Convex via `PushGmailTokenToConvex`, the server-side connect endpoint just needs to check if `gmailCredentials` exist.

